    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/InfinitySweeper.png\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" alt=\"'经典扫雷肉鸽游戏标题'\" /></span><strong>扫雷×肉鸽=无限挑战！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无限扫雷</strong>将经典扫雷玩法与Roguelite元素结合，带来永久死亡、随机生成关卡和策略成长的颠覆性体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/Sequence_01_3.gif\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" alt=\"'动态玩法演示'\" /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >揭开方块、预判陷阱、收集强化——每一步都关乎生死！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/featuers.png\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" alt=\"'特色系统图标'\" /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>革新性扫雷玩法</strong>: Roguelite机制+永久强化，打破传统规则</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无限随机地图</strong>: 算法生成独一无二的关卡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>深度策略计算</strong>: 分析敌人AI模式，规划最优路径</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>硬核生存挑战</strong>: 适合解谜与Roguelite爱好者</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/Sequence_01_4.gif\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" alt=\"'高分挑战演示'\" /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >利用数据统计优化策略，<i><strong>不断突破极限！</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/gameplay.png\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" alt=\"'界面解析'\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你是怀旧扫雷玩家还是现代Roguelite爱好者，<strong>无限扫雷</strong>都将带来令人上瘾的全新体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/Sequence_01_5.gif\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" alt=\"'无限模式预告'\" /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >标记地雷、计算概率、存活到最后——这才是终极扫雷！</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/Sequence_01_6.gif\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" alt=\"'Boss战演示'\" /></span></h2>",
